GNU VCDImager README
--------------------

see texinfo documentation for more information

see http://www.hvrlab.dhs.org/~hvr/vcdimager/ for latest news,
information and how to subscribe to mailing lists for VCDImager.

please report any bugs you encounter

information for CD-i support:

get "Video-CD on CD-i 4.1.1" from http://www.icdia.org/sw_app/, unpack
that zip file into some directory, which needs to be given to
vcdimager in order to find those files, using the 
`--with-cdi=' commandline option.

hvr
--
